1144
01:36:42.694 --> 01:36:44.277
<i>Itulah kegunaan anugerah.</i>

1145
01:36:47.156 --> 01:36:49.032
<i>Saya beri satu pada mak cik Brenda.</i>

1146
01:36:50.284 --> 01:36:52.077
<i>Supaya sekarang dia boleh rock.</i>

1147
01:36:56.791 --> 01:36:58.834
<i>Saya mahu pak cik Bub dapat satu.</i>

1148
01:37:01.295 --> 01:37:02.671
<i>Dan Cik Crudstaff.</i>

1149
01:37:04.799 --> 01:37:08.927
